Package: emmbars
Title: Add Emmeans Significance Brackets to ggplot Objects
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Nicholas",
           family = "Edenhoffer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "NicholasEdenhoffer@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Provides add_emmeans_pbars(), a convenience wrapper that adds
    statistical significance brackets to ggplot objects using post hoc
    comparisons generated by emmeans::pairs() or emmeans::contrast().
    Bracket positions are inferred automatically from the plot structure,
    with support for facets, nested facets, dodged geoms, and fill/color
    aesthetics.
